<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Package Delivered - CMS</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: white; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #20c997); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; }
        .success-icon { font-size: 60px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
        .delivery-details { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; }
        .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 10px 0; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
        .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .detail-label { font-weight: 600; color: #495057; }
        .detail-value { color: #28a745; font-weight: 500; }
        .celebration { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ffed4e); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .feedback-button { display: inline-block; background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 600; margin: 10px; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="success-icon">üéâ</div>
            <h1>Package Delivered!</h1>
            <p>Your package has been successfully delivered</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
            
            <p>Great news! We're excited to inform you that your package has been successfully delivered!</p>
            
            <div class="celebration">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">‚úÖ Delivery Confirmed</h3>
                <p style="color: #856404; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;">Package {{refNumber}} has reached its destination</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="delivery-details">
                <h3>üì¶ Delivery Details</h3>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Package Reference:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{refNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Tracking ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{trackingId}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Delivered On:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{deliveryDate}}</span>
                </div>
                
                {{#if recipientName}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Received By:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{recipientName}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Delivered By:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{deliveredBy}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border: 1px solid #90caf9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976d2;">üåü How Was Your Experience?</h4>
                <p style="color: #1976d2;">We'd love to hear about your delivery experience with CMS</p>
                <a href="#" class="feedback-button">‚≠ê Rate Our Service</a>
                <a href="#" class="feedback-button">üìù Leave Feedback</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">üìã Important Notes</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #856404;">
                    <li>Please verify the contents of your package</li>
                    <li>Keep this email as proof of delivery</li>
                    <li>Contact us immediately if there are any issues</li>
                    <li>Your tracking ID remains valid for future reference</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing CMS for your delivery needs. We appreciate your trust in our services and look forward to serving you again!</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about your delivery, please don't hesitate to contact our customer support team.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The CMS Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>CMS - Courier Management System</strong></p>
            <p>Fast, Reliable, Secure Delivery Services</p>
            
            <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">üìß Email Support</a> |
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">üìû Call Support</a> |
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">üåê Website</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
                This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.<br>
                For support, contact us at support@cms.com or call 1800-123-4567
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 